# Discourse on the Worship of Priapus Worship of the Generative Powers Index

------------------------------------------------------------------------

The 1865 printing of Richard Payne Knights' 1786 essay on Priapus
worship was filled out with an additional essay by Thomas Wright. This
page indexes both of these texts.

The complete title of the 1865 work was:

A discourse on the worship of Priapus, and its connection with the
mystic theology of the ancients by Richard Payne Knight. To which is
added an essay on the worship of the generative powers during the Middle
Ages of western Europe.

[A Discourse on the Worship of Priapus](dwp/index.md)  
by Richard Payne Knight \[1786\]

[The Worship of the Generative Powers](wgp/index.md)  
BY Thomas Wright \[1865\]
